text: Nina Dobrev (born on January 9, 1989 in Sofia, Bulgaria) is a Bulgarian- Canadian actress. She is best known for playing the role of Elena Gilbert and Katherine Pierce on the dramatic television series, The Vampire Diaries. == Biography == Nina Dobrev was born on January 9, 1989 in Sofia, Bulgaria to Bulgarian parents. Her father is a computer scientist, and her mother is an artist. Her family moved to Canada when she was two years old. She was raised in Toronto, Ontario. She was 20 years old when she started her first show. ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:Canadian television actors Category:Canadian movie actors Category:Actors from Sofia Category:1989 births Category:Living people Category:Canadian voice actors
